"kho amhākaṃ hetu adhammacārī visamacārī ahosi, mā naṃ nirayaṃ nirayapālā’”ti?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn97:12.3"
msgid "“No hidaṃ, bho sāriputta."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn97:12.4"
msgid "Atha kho naṃ vikkandantaṃyeva niraye nirayapālā pakkhipeyyuṃ”."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya13"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc10"></a>
msgctxt "mn97:13.1"
msgid ""
"“Taṃ kiṃ maññasi, dhanañjāni, idhekacco devatānaṃ hetu adhammacārī "
"visamacārī assa, tamenaṃ adhammacariyāvisamacariyāhetu nirayaṃ nirayapālā "
"upakaḍḍheyyuṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn97:13.2"
msgid ""
"Labheyya nu kho so ‘ahaṃ kho devatānaṃ hetu adhammacārī visamacārī ahosiṃ, "
"mā maṃ nirayaṃ nirayapālā’ti, devatā vā panassa labheyyuṃ ‘eso kho amhākaṃ "
"hetu adhammacārī visamacārī ahosi, mā naṃ nirayaṃ nirayapālā’”ti?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn97:13.3"
msgid "“No hidaṃ, bho sāriputta."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn97:13.4"
msgid "Atha kho naṃ vikkandantaṃyeva niraye nirayapālā pakkhipeyyuṃ”."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya14"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc11"></a>
msgctxt "mn97:14.1"
msgid ""
"“Taṃ kiṃ maññasi, dhanañjāni, idhekacco rañño hetu adhammacārī visamacārī "
"assa, tamenaṃ adhammacariyāvisamacariyāhetu nirayaṃ nirayapālā upakaḍḍheyyuṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn97:14.2"
msgid ""
"Labheyya nu kho so ‘ahaṃ kho rañño hetu adhammacārī visamacārī ahosiṃ, mā "
"maṃ nirayaṃ nirayapālā’ti, rājā vā panassa labheyya ‘eso kho amhākaṃ hetu "
"adhammacārī visamacārī ahosi, mā naṃ nirayaṃ nirayapālā’”ti?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn97:14.3"
msgid "“No hidaṃ, bho sāriputta."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn97:14.4"
msgid "Atha kho naṃ vikkandantaṃyeva niraye nirayapālā pakkhipeyyuṃ”."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya15"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc12"></a>
msgctxt "mn97:15.1"
msgid ""
"“Taṃ kiṃ maññasi, dhanañjāni, idhekacco kāyassa pīṇanāhetu brūhanāhetu "
"adhammacārī visamacārī assa, tamenaṃ adhammacariyāvisamacariyāhetu nirayaṃ "
"nirayapālā upakaḍḍheyyuṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn97:15.2"
msgid ""
"Labheyya nu kho so ‘ahaṃ kho kāyassa pīṇanāhetu brūhanāhetu adhammacārī "
"visamacārī ahosiṃ, mā maṃ nirayaṃ nirayapālā’ti, pare vā panassa labheyyuṃ ‘"
"eso kho kāyassa pīṇanāhetu brūhanāhetu adhammacārī visamacārī ahosi, mā naṃ "
"nirayaṃ nirayapālā’”ti?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn97:15.3"
msgid "“No hidaṃ, bho sāriputta."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn97:15.4"
msgid "Atha kho naṃ vikkandantaṃyeva niraye nirayapālā pakkhipeyyuṃ”."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya16"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc13"></a>
msgctxt "mn97:16.1"
msgid ""
"“Taṃ kiṃ maññasi, dhanañjāni, yo vā mātāpitūnaṃ hetu adhammacārī visamacārī "
"assa, yo vā mātāpitūnaṃ hetu dhammacārī samacārī assa;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn97:16.2"
msgid "katamaṃ seyyo”ti?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn97:16.3"
msgid ""
"“Yo hi, bho sāriputta, mātāpitūnaṃ hetu adhammacārī visamacārī assa, na taṃ "
"seyyo;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn97:16.4"
msgid ""
"yo ca kho, bho sāriputta, mātāpitūnaṃ hetu dhammacārī samacārī assa, "
"tadevettha seyyo."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn97:16.5"
msgid ""
"Adhammacariyāvisamacariyāhi, bho sāriputta, dhammacariyāsamacariyā seyyo”ti."
msgstr ""

# Reading anne for annesam as in PTS edition. otherwise it would be “others have livelihoods …”
msgctxt "mn97:16.6"
msgid ""
"“Atthi kho, dhanañjāni, aññesaṃ hetukā dhammikā kammantā, yehi sakkā "
"mātāpitaro ceva posetuṃ, na ca pāpakammaṃ kātuṃ, puññañca paṭipadaṃ "
"paṭipajjituṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
